<plot>The final installment of the Lovindapocalypse series finds Angela Bettis and Kevin Ford turning their focus on the people in the world around them more than ever. Wildfires ravish California, a movie-star is elected as Governor of their state, and their country is in a permanent state of war. More political and full of interviews, L3 is different than its predecessors in that it finds our loving couple trying desperately to ascend into another dimension</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?346038</url></doc>
